end.[event code], qSoloVend.[Securities Received], qSoloVend.Anomalo, qSoloVend.NonAnomalo, qSoloVend.[Anomalous Date], qSoloVend.Verificato, qSoloVend.[Checked Date], qSoloVend.[Budget No_], qSoloVend.DataDecorrenza, qSoloVend.KimoOrder, [Sales Header Extension].[Old Order No_], qSoloVend.[Season Code], qSoloVend.[Transport Reason Code], qSoloVend.TransportReasonCodeDescription, qSoloVend.[Location Code], qSoloVend.[Shipping Agent Code], qSoloVend.[Shipping Agent Service Code], qSoloVend.[Date Reservation], qSoloVend.[Fast Shipping], [Ship-to Address].[Geographical Zone 2], [Ship-to Address].[Country_Region Code], qSoloVend.CommissionGroupCodeOrder, [Sales Header Extension].[Special Requests], Customer.[Purchase Group], Customer.[Distribution Channel], qSoloVend.GeographicalZoneFromOrder, qSoloVend.GeographicalZoneDescriptionFromOrder, qSoloVend.[Budget Area], qSoloVend.[Model Cross Reference], qSoloVend.[trademark code];

